#5801
The Path of Enlightenment: Wayfinder~
There are many commands, some of which you will use a lot and some of which will
rarely cross your screen. On the Path of Enlightenment you will learn the most
basic and most useful commands, and some of the principles of a text-based game.
Most commands can be abbreviated to one or more letters, since it is tedious to
repeatedly type out a command over and over. The basic movement commands are
north, east, south, west, up, and down, each of which shorten to their first
letter. Try following the path east to your next lesson.
