The Path of Enlightenment: Vision~
Use the 'look' command to view the room you are in. The entire world is made of
a series of "rooms", each representing a small area of the game. Someone seems
to have dropped their bag here- go ahead and take it, if its on the ground it's
yours. Type 'get bag' to pick up the bag, which puts it in your 'inventory'. 
Use 'examine' to look at an object and its contents, using the syntax 'examine
<object>'.
