The Path of Enlightenment: Possessions~
You now have in your possession, if you got it in the last room, a bag and 25
gold coins. Use 'inventory' to see the items you currently carry on your
person, and 'equipment' to see what items you are wearing. Good god, you're
running around in your skivvies! Fortunately, a shop keeper has been positioned
here to help passersby with such a problem as this. Use 'list' to see what
goods are for sale and for how much. Use 'buy <item#>' to fork over the gold in
return for that item. It is suggested that you buy one of each item before
going down. By the way, 'wear all' - you have got some equipment already.
