The Path of Enlightenment: Possessions II~
If you followed the instructions of the last room and bought one of everything,
you should have a canteen, a hat, the prodding stick, a pair of sandals, faded
blue jeans, and a flannel shirt. Use the 'wear' command to wear equipment,
'hold' to hold the canteen, and 'wield' to wield the stick. Different items are
used in different ways: the clothing is meant to be worn, the canteen holds
water to drink from when held, and the stick is your first weapon. Proceed west
when you have tried these commands.
