The Path of Enlightenment: Persona~
Use the 'score' command to view your personal status. Such information as your
name, your level, and spell affects will appear. Notice the spot for saving
throws and armor class: those kinds of scores you want to decrease, as the lower
they are, the lower the chance of you being fully affected by an attack (saving
throws for special attacks, armor class for melee attacks). Your Hit points,
Mana, and moVements are displayed in your prompt, above the bar where you put in
commands.
~
