#5808
The Path of Enlightenment: Growth~
You will grow more powerful and more knowledgeable with time, maybe become a
legendary player. Right now, right here, you can learn the tools of your trade,
the skills of warriors and thieves and the spells of clerics and mages. You can
only practice skills and spells of your level and class, and this consumes
practices which you should have. Don't expect to train everything to the max
right now, but get ones that will help you raise your level. Use the 'practice'
command to see what you can practice, and 'practice <skill>'.
~
