The Path of Enlightenment: Identity~
Type 'score'- this will display your basic statistics. These will change with
time, as you level up (this affects Hp, Mana, moVements, and sometimes Armor
Class, Hit roll, and Damage roll), as you decide whether you want to be good,
neutral, or evil (this is your alignment, which ranges from -1000 to 1000).
As you get closer to the light, your shadow becomes more defined. Fight!
