The Path of Enlightenment: Socialization!~
What's a massive multiplayer game without a little communication? Fortunately,
we gods have provided you with diverse means of communication, the most basic of
which are 'say <message>' and socials such as hug, wave, and explode. There are
other methods of communication as well, and just about anything you can imagine
to do is a social- if it isn't a social already, suggest it to a god, and it
will be one soon! Read 'help communication' for more information on this topic.
