The End of the Path: Do's and Do-NOT's~
To get an overview of the do's and dont's, type <policy>. These are a few
rules, which must be abided by for you to be allowed to stay. We try to keep
them short and to the point. The last command you'll learn here is 'recall'. 
This will transport you to the center of the main city. From here on out, you
are your own guide. If you need help, just ask around- may the gods of Kuvia
look favorably upon you in your exploits. Type 'recall' or head south into the
guildhall to leave this place and move on to greener pastures.
~
